name: Recreate a waiting after voiding ticket

steps.name: Given I am on the HOME page
When I wait for the page fully loaded
And I navigate to "WAIT" on the navigation bar
Then I should be redirected to CREATE_WAITING page
And I should see the text "Create Waiting" visible
Then I should see the categories displayed correctly in check-in
And I should see the services displayed correctly in check-in
And I should see the "Next Available Service" service
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('li.ItemService').getByText('Next Available Service', { exact: true })
When I click to create new customer with the default loyalty program "2 Points = $1"
Expect "toBeVisible" getByRole('button', { name: 'Click Here To Add Customers', exact: true })
Click getByRole('button', { name: 'Click Here To Add Customers', exact: true })
Wait for selector locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) })
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) })
And I create the new customer name "Recreate"
Wait for selector locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) })
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) })

Expect "toBeVisible" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) }).locator('div.MuiDialogActions-root').getByRole('button', { name: 'Save', exact: true })

Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) }).locator('div.MuiDialogActions-root').getByRole('button', { name: 'Save', exact: true })
Expect "not toBeVisible" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#draggable-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Create New Customer' }) })
When I select the "FULL SET & FILL IN" category
Expect "toHaveText" locator('button.MuiButtonBase-root').getByText('FULL SET & FILL IN', { exact: true })
Click locator('button.MuiButtonBase-root').getByText('FULL SET & FILL IN', { exact: true })
When I add the "Full set" service to my cart
Then I should see a popup dialog with title "Pick Technician"
When I click on the "Anna" text inside the content section of the opening dialog
Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title') }).locator('div.MuiDialogContent-root').getByText('Anna', { exact: true }).last()
Then I should see the service "Full set" in my cart
And I should see the duration "25 mins" in my cart
When I click on the "SAVE" button
And I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should see the selected "WAITING LIST" tab on the Home page
When I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should see the customer "Recreate" in the waiting list
And I should see the service "Full set" in the waiting list
And I should see the technician "Anna" in the waiting list
When I wait for the page fully loaded
And I click on the first row for customer "Recreate" to expand details
And I select the "Create Ticket" on the Daily Task
And I wait for the page fully loaded
Then I should see the "Ticket View" screen
And I should see the "Manicure" service
And I should see the user info "Anna" in the ticket
When I wait for the page fully loaded
And I click on the "Void Ticket" button
Expect "toBeVisible" getByRole('button', { name: 'Void Ticket', exact: true })
Click getByRole('button', { name: 'Void Ticket', exact: true })
And I click on the "confirm" button in the popup dialog
Then I should see the selected "SERVICE" tab on the Home page
When I select the "WAITING LIST" tab
And I wait for the page fully loaded
And I click on the first row for customer "Recreate" to expand details
And I select the "Create Ticket" on the Daily Task
Then I should see the "Ticket View" screen
When I pay the exact amount by "Cash"
Expect "toBeVisible" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Close Ticket' }) })
Expect "toContainText" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Close Ticket' }) }).locator('div.MuiDialogContent-root')
Expect "toContainText" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Close Ticket' }) }).locator('div.MuiDialogContent-root')

Click locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Close Ticket' }) }).locator('div.MuiDialogActions-root').getByRole('button', { name: 'OK', exact: true })
Expect "toBeHidden" locator('div[role="dialog"]').filter({ has: locator('#alert-dialog-title').filter({ hasText: 'Close Ticket' }) })
Then I should see the selected "SERVICE" tab on the Home page
